== 得獎 ==
2002年，Crytek因極地戰嚎遊戲獲得的獎項：
* [[E3电子娱乐展|E3]] Best Action Runner up
* E3 Technological Excellence Runner up
* E3 Best Surprise Runner up

2003年，極地戰嚎釋出並獲得：
* [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] "The top ten of PC GAME E3
* [[ECTS|ECTS]] Best PC Game
* [[IGN|IGN]] E3 Best Action Runner up
* IGN E3 Technological Excellence Runner up

2004年，Crytek獲得「企業卓越獎項」（Industry Excellence Awards）：
* Best New European Studio
* Best Independent Developer
* Best New PC IP - Far Cry<ref name="Crytek Awards">{{cite web | url = http://www.crytek.com/news/news/browse/6/article/9/3-industry/download//d713af5ac0.html | title = Crytek Awards | accessdate = 2008-01-03 | archive-date = 2019-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190626164049/https://www.crytek.com/news/news/browse/6/article/9/3-industry/download//d713af5ac0.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

數個月後，得到四項德國開發者獎項：
* Best Full Price Game
* Best Game Design
* Best Technology
* Best Graphic<ref name="Crysis Awards">{{cite web | url = http://www.crytek.com/news/news/browse/6/article/9/crytek-won-4/download//55d84493a7.html | title = Crysis Awards | accessdate = 2008-01-03 | archive-date = 2019-06-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190621144238/https://www.crytek.com/news/news/browse/6/article/9/crytek-won-4/download//55d84493a7.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

同年7月，Crytek在五個獎項獲得亞軍：
* Best PC game
* Use of online
* Art and Sound
* New Euro Studio (Debut Title)
* Independent Developer.

2005年，Crytek獲得[[GDC|GDC]]（Game Developers Conference）的「2004年最佳工作室」獎項。

